00:06:57.540 --> 00:07:01.410
Uh, she went back to work.

00:07:01.410 --> 00:07:03.160
Which one do you want?

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.200
The one with the strawberry!

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:09.080
That witch! She sent me on errands
so she could talk alone with him!

00:07:09.080 --> 00:07:12.700
