by my first name since 6th grade.

00:07:12.700 --> 00:07:15.080
It felt kinda awkward.

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:17.120
Wait, what?

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.200
She used my first name.

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.700
I heard you the first time!

00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:23.120
