00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:45.660
I mean, you were watching
the guys change at school.

00:07:45.660 --> 00:07:48.330
Yeah, but I had a reason.

00:07:48.330 --> 00:07:52.790
Wait, do you have a crush
on someone or something?

00:07:57.200 --> 00:07:59.500
No, it's because...

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:05.120
My <i>name</i>?!

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:07.910
That's what you've been so worried about?!

00:08:07.910 --> 00:08:10.500
My name though, really? Wow.

