00:08:32.330 --> 00:08:33.660
--I can read it!
--Hand it back.

00:08:33.660 --> 00:08:39.790
Whatever, I'm keeping this,
just in case I forget it again.

00:08:39.790 --> 00:08:42.410
I'd really rather you didn't forget it.

00:08:42.410 --> 00:08:44.830
I-I know, okay?!

00:08:44.830 --> 00:08:47.500
You'll remember it easier if you say it!

00:08:48.500 --> 00:08:50.830
I-Izumi.

00:08:50.830 --> 00:08:54.410
That's right, Hori-san.

00:08:58.290 --> 00:09:02.500
No, it feels weird.
I'll just keep calling you Miyamura!

00:09:02.500 --> 00:09:05.370
Oh, c'mon, Hori-san...

00:09:05.370 --> 00:09:06.700
Hold up, Miyamura!

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:09.580
Do <i>you </i>not know <i>my </i>first name?!

00:09:09.580 --> 00:09:12.000
What? It's Kyoko, right?

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:16.330
I look like a total moron!

00:09:16.330 --> 00:09:19.580
Sometimes, Hori-san says the dumbest things.

00:09:19.580 --> 00:09:22.330
W-Well, start laughing! I know it's funny!

00:09:22.330 --> 00:09:24.540
But you'll get mad at me if I laugh.

00:09:24.540 --> 00:09:26.410
Yeah, I will!

00:09:27.450 --> 00:09:29.330
That's no fair!

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:40.040
Sorry about all this, Hori-san.
I know you're already so busy.

00:09:40.040 --> 00:09:43.580
It's totally fine! I'd do
anything for you, Sengoku-kun.

00:09:43.580 --> 00:09:47.120
Thanks, you're a lifesaver.

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:50.040
