00:10:41.290 --> 00:10:44.330
Sure, but they need the help, so I don't mind.

00:10:44.330 --> 00:10:46.700
What?! You should!

00:10:46.700 --> 00:10:48.160
She's got it rough.

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:49.370
Yeah.

00:10:49.370 --> 00:10:54.370
And we're too dumb to help out with anything.

00:10:54.370 --> 00:10:55.910
Yeah.

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:59.450
President Sengoku's top of the class, right?

00:10:59.450 --> 00:11:01.330
Really?

00:11:01.330 --> 00:11:03.330
The girls all like him, too.

00:11:03.330 --> 00:11:08.120
Maybe Hori-san's helping
him out because she likes him.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:18.950
Hori-san, you around?

00:11:18.950 --> 00:11:21.450
Oh, Ayasaki-san!

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.750
Here are the files and notebooks I worked on.

00:11:28.750 --> 00:11:30.700
Watch out, they're heavy.

00:11:30.700 --> 00:11:33.790
I've got 'em! Thanks!

00:11:33.790 --> 00:11:36.410
Whoa, she's gorgeous!

00:11:36.410 --> 00:11:38.910
