the hot girl's work onto you, Hori!

00:11:51.790 --> 00:11:54.160
Jeez, don't put it like that.

00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:56.410
Though you're right,

00:11:56.410 --> 00:11:59.040
the work I just did <i>was</i>
Ayasaki-san's responsibility.

00:11:59.040 --> 00:12:02.750
They're totally making her do her work...

00:12:10.120 --> 00:12:13.200
I'm gonna head home.

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:15.500
Okay.

00:12:15.500 --> 00:12:19.540
I hope Hori-san's okay...

00:12:22.580 --> 00:12:26.290
