00:15:00.120 --> 00:15:02.540
C'mon, just say sorry.

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:03.910
Ishikawa-kun.

00:15:03.910 --> 00:15:04.830
Miyamura?

00:15:04.830 --> 00:15:09.370
Can you hold my bag and glasses? Thanks.

00:15:09.370 --> 00:15:12.450
Well, Hori-san?

00:15:16.700 --> 00:15:17.250
--I'm--

00:15:17.250 --> 00:15:18.370
